This project was designed to complement the board game [Codenames](http://www.czechgames.com/en/codenames/) by 
reducing the amount of set up time between games. The artwork/gameplay was developed by the creators of the game. 
A generic word list is used by default inside the resources folder but it's highly reccomended that the list be replaced by the 
actual Codenames word list for a better game experience.

### Usage

-   At the start of the game, 25 words are randomly chosen from the word list.
-   When a word is guessed, click the button until the appropriate graphic is displayed.
-   At the end of a game click the Randomize button to reset the board and randomly select 25 new words.

### Details

This project is maintained [here](https://github.com/mjholt02/CodeNames) and was built using Java,JavaFX, and the NetBeans IDE.
